➜正面挑战日系街车，9.98万元起售，第七代伊兰特正式上市
http://www.sohu.com/a/428144956_99994080	30289
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201029/501e3074a34e474ebb4341cbd163005b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201029/e5a6f065d9b94720b2d1fd958cb91f57.png" max-width="600" /></p>
