➜美系大块头上线！改头换面升级发动机，深度试驾新款雪佛兰探界者
http://www.sohu.com/a/428131896_99994080	32691
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201029/48344a6a64e1409b833e9b3e3527f9f0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201029/89f2569a81464802828ce1559d25fbfa.png" max-width="600" /></p>
